{"tid":1199651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩開Aoc，想討論戰術","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:41:05.000Z","uid":150907,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a2dd4b8a1c3c757a98cd0fe4f784be600e864e","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"其實歷史上，以少勝多嘅戰役。<br />\n<br />\n多數係知自己條team有乜人，可以分成乜人一堆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熟識地型，用自己比較強嘅打對方比較弱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n速度快嘅有法國騎兵喺外圍得閒走下得閒虛攻下，引走對手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大隻嘅有印度戰象肉搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲有嘅咪英國長弓兵外投，仲有牧師苦口婆心嘅勸告不過多數人地理L你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗外國嘢，中國嘢三國兵法，聲東擊西，暗渡陳倉啊都幾好㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一支軍隊咪一大堆一齊，最好就分123456789組，用鄭九組就最好，每段都開戲，爽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世紀帝國AOC真喺好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三國志都好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw想去立法局參觀，各位師兄師姐知唔知網頁上邊有冇地圖介紹㗎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好有附近點走，可以去埋其他景點嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968d5fec7d4a1b198d9c5e1b4ea5398885be1420","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4baa00ac1c23418acee6464be96463b109d947","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"想開戰前瘋狂11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61936affd73f7755f11efa263bdceb35e787e763","tid":1199651,"uid":178072,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"新手可以先試試27匃奴城快，容錯率高又易爆肉馬"},{"pid":"135fe12157720f278c2a29c95688c46214171f9d","tid":1199651,"uid":203476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"新手<br />\n聽日試下玩法國騎兵先"},{"pid":"630620aaf413a2049f8d099d8a8446891cf6f904","tid":1199651,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"咪膠啦，武力咁唔對等點打"},{"pid":"b192617664f66ad8746a2bff1b3f5b22821bde98","tid":1199651,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d119500db9715f137b762cc312304dadcbdbd1","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"希望戰象搵返戰象，法國騎兵搵返法國騎兵，group埋一齊行會好慢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474971d25f58dbcb5f30626151581c2631822a7f","tid":1199651,"uid":15090