gry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔好走埋一堆，人地出投石車就一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3c06ce166b2dd646efe0938f1065a59d6c19ca","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"最好分幾團兵，不斷出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咁聽到戰鼓聲，對手疲於奔命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22af4e46fad9742b21502eafb1ad672e8fd1cae0","tid":1199651,"uid":158645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"你黑暗時代點打人哋帝王<br />\n起碼升到城堡先好講戰術<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係10隻民兵都打唔贏1隻條武"},{"pid":"f8f4051be9e0925b7041a4b10fffc42652455d73","tid":1199651,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"城鎮居民嘅強項係瘋狂起野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑暗時代起下木牆當城牆咁用，起得多點都擋到D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bb1bea2da4f7231932a9206601d130ab38ca32","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22af4e46fad9742b21502eafb1ad672e8fd1cae0","tid":1199651,"uid":158645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"你黑暗時代點打人哋帝王<br />\n起碼升到城堡先好講戰術<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係10隻民兵都打唔贏1隻條武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"師兄，識玩，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無方法十六分鐘城快，攻入市民中心先，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後再諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8402bf12a1f8a53067608495b9985bd87116088f","tid":1199651,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f4051be9e0925b7041a4b10fffc42652455d73","tid":1199651,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"城鎮居民嘅強項係瘋狂起野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑暗時代起下木牆